org.funcito.mode.Mode

  • Packages that use Mode 
    Package Description
    org.funcito
    Funcito is a method-wrapping library for Java, to assist in using several Java functional programming frameworks.
    org.funcito.collectionsgeneric
    Funcito public interface into the collections-generic API.
    org.funcito.functionaljava
    Funcito public interface into the Functional Java API.
    org.funcito.functorfactory  
    org.funcito.guava
    Funcito public interface into the Gooogle Guava API.
    org.funcito.jedi
    Funcito public interface into the Jedi API.
    org.funcito.mode
    Mode and TypedMode interfaces and core implementations.
    org.funcito.play
    Funcito public interface into the Play! Framework 2 API.

    Funcito public interface into the Netflix RxJava API.

    • Uses of Mode in org.funcito.mode

      Classes in org.funcito.mode that implement Mode 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  NoOp
      This Mode provides a plain, unadorned BasicFunctor
      class  SafeNav
      This Mode provides a SafeNavFunctor with an implicit null default value
      class  ValidateNullBoolean
      This mode is internally used by Funcito for 3rd party APIs with primitive boolean-returning predicates, returning a NullValidatingPredicate that will help diagnose execution problems rather than simply throwing NullPointerException deep in the Funcito internals.
